        "textColor": "#9a9994",
        "fontFamily": "unknown",
        "align": "left"
      },
      "frameId": "f-3",
      "visualKind": "text",
      "title": "<p>Who is the target persona?</p><p>What are their jobs-to-be-done?</p><p>What are their current workarounds or competing solutions?</p><p>Who is out of scope?</p>"
    },
    {
      "id": "n-22",
      "position": {
        "x": 292.218485384052,
        "y": 149.14285714285882
      },
      "size": {
        "width": 520.4369707714286
      },
      "style": {
        "fontSize": 18,
        "textColor": "#9a9994",
        "fontFamily": "unknown",
        "align": "left"
      },
      "frameId": "f-4",
      "visualKind": "text",
      "title": "<p>How will we measure success?</p><p>What key business outcomes will this drive?</p><p>What will signal that we&#39;re on the right track?</p><p>What must we watch to avoid negative impacts?</p>"
    },
    {
      "id": "n-23",
      "position": {
        "x": 292.2184853840481,
        "y": 149.14285714285882
      },
      "size": {
        "width": 520.4369707714286
      },
      "style": {
        "fontSize": 18,
        "textColor": "#9a9994",
        "fontFamily": "unknown",
        "align": "left"
      },
      "frameId": "f-5",
      "visualKind": "text",
      "title": "<p>How might we best solve the core user problem?</p><p>What does the ideal user journey look like?</p><p>What are the essential components of this solution?</p><p>What are our biggest, riskiest assumptions to test?</p>"
    },
    {
      "id": "n-24",
      "position": {
        "x": 292.21848538404834,
        "y": 149.14285714285893
      },
      "size": {
